---
import { SITE_CONFIG } from '../data/config';
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="bg-accent text-gray-100 pt-32 pb-16 relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary via-secondary to-primary opacity-50"></div>
  
  <div class="container mx-auto">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-16 mb-24">
      <div class="lg:col-span-2">
        <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8 group">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-secondary flex items-center justify-center rounded-2xl border-2 border-primary shadow-lg shadow-primary/10 group-hover:rotate-12 transition-transform">
            <span class="text-primary font-black text-2xl">V</span>
          </div>
          <span class="text-3xl font-black text-white tracking-widest leading-none">
            {SITE_CONFIG.nap.name.split(' ')[0].toUpperCase()} <br/> <span class="text-primary italic">{SITE_CONFIG.nap.name.split(' ').slice(1).join(' ').toUpperCase()}</span>
          </span>
        </a>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-xl max-w-md leading-relaxed mb-10 font-medium italic">
          "Transformando a Baía de Todos os Santos com a clareza e elegância do vidro temperado de alta performance."
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <a href="https://instagram.com" target="_blank" class="w-12 h-12 bg-white/5 hover:bg-primary hover:text-secondary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center transition-all border border-white/10 hover:scale-110 active:scale-95 shadow-xl">
             <span class="font-black text-xs uppercase">Ig</span>
          </a>
          <a href="https://facebook.com" target="_blank" class="w-12 h-12 bg-white/5 hover:bg-primary hover:text-secondary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center transition-all border border-white/10 hover:scale-110 active:scale-95 shadow-xl">
            <span class="font-black text-xs uppercase">Fb</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div>
        <h4 class="font-black text-lg mb-10 text-primary uppercase tracking-[0.3em] border-l-4 border-primary pl-4">Navegação</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-6">
          <li><a href="/" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-white hover:translate-x-3 flex items-center gap-2 transition-all font-bold">Início</a></li>
          <li><a href="/servicos" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-white hover:translate-x-3 flex items-center gap-2 transition-all font-bold">Serviços</a></li>
          <li><a href="/sobre" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-white hover:translate-x-3 flex items-center gap-2 transition-all font-bold">A Empresa</a></li>
          <li><a href="/blog" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-white hover:translate-x-3 flex items-center gap-2 transition-all font-bold">Dicas Técnicas</a></li>
          <li><a href="/contato" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-white hover:translate-x-3 flex items-center gap-2 transition-all font-bold text-primary">Orçamentos</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div>
        <h4 class="font-black text-lg mb-10 text-primary uppercase tracking-[0.3em] border-l-4 border-primary pl-4">Matriz {SITE_CONFIG.nap.location.city}</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-6 text-gray-300 font-medium">
          <li class="flex gap-4">
            <span class="text-primary font-black">📍</span>
            {SITE_CONFIG.nap.address}
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href={`tel:55${SITE_CONFIG.nap.whatsapp}`} class="flex gap-4 hover:text-primary transition-colors">
              <span class="text-primary font-black">📞</span>
              {SITE_CONFIG.nap.phone}
            </a>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-4">
            <span class="text-primary font-black">✉️</span>
            {SITE_CONFIG.nap.email}
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="border-t border-white/5 pt-12 flex flex-col lg:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-8 text-gray-500 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">
      <p>&copy; {year} Vidraçaria Salvador. Todos os direitos reservados.</p>
      <div class="flex gap-10">
        <a href="/privacidade" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">Privacidade</a>
        <a href="/termos" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">Termos de Uso</a>
      </div>
      <p class="flex items-center gap-2">
        Feito com <span class="text-primary text-xl">⚡</span> por Astro
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
